{"tid":2360864,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"倪晨曦公開生B過程：順產比我想像中痛1000萬倍","createTime":"2021-01-10T07:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T08:17:35.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"227aedc77014751a0174dc5bb8f3e54de1cb2951","tid":2360864,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20210109/s00009/0944525ace166c98c0615998827fb2f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20210109%2Fs00009%2F0944525ace166c98c0615998827fb2f2.jpg&h=5cfb8e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倪晨曦今次公開生B過程，是想幫所有的準媽媽們打氣。（倪晨曦Instagram圖片／明報製圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20210109/s00009/09452521917a93b6ec42af47f258d5c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20210109%2Fs00009%2F09452521917a93b6ec42af47f258d5c2.jpg&h=e9ac15af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倪晨曦獲得老公吳嘉釗在旁支持安慰。（倪晨曦Instagram圖片／明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n倪晨曦（Elva）去年12月為老公吳嘉釗誕下兒子Virgil，今日在網上分享她的生B過程，除了經歷陣痛外，大爆BB頭部方向不對，子宮頸度數不足，並親自為BB剪臍帶，讓大家感受到當媽媽的偉大。<br />\n<br />\n倪晨曦留言：「用了一個月的時間來緩神，再一個月的時間才能看回之前的影片，終於你們很想知道的生產日記來了！順產比我想像中痛1000萬倍，也不知道當初去何來的勇氣，不過我想說聽一些勵志的故事是很重要的，還好當初身邊有5個朋友都有非常順利的生產故事，幫我加強了一些信心，膽粗粗的直接就決定自己來。在臨生之前我也經常和寶寶聊天，我和他說媽媽和你一起加油，你用自己的力量，媽媽會幫你一起來到這個世上，最後我們都成功了！雖然很痛但也覺得很奇妙，身體可以做出這麼多不可思議的事，這些經歷都是讓我在不斷的成長，其實無論是順產還是開刀，能母子平安生下健康的寶寶已經很不容易。這支影片想幫所有的準媽媽們打氣！ #人生最痛 #痛並快樂著」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20210109/1610199066412/%E5%80%AA%E6%99%A8%E6%9B%A6%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%94%9Fb%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B-%E9%A0%86%E7%94%A2%E6%AF%94%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E5%83%8F%E4%B8%AD%E7%97%9B1000%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20210109%2F1610199066412%2F%25E5%2580%25AA%25E6%2599%25A8%25E6%259B%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2594%259Fb%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B-%25E9%25A0%2586%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25AF%2594%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%2583%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2597%259B1000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258D&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=ce8bff26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20210109%2F1610199066412%2F%25E5%2580%25AA%25E6%2599%25A8%25E6%259B%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2594%259Fb%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B-%25E9%25A0%2586%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25AF%2594%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%2583%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2597%259B1000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258D&h=a85df572\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20210109/1610199066412/%E5%80%AA%E6%99%A8%E6%9B%A6%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%94%9Fb%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B-%E9%A0%86%E7%94%A2%E6%AF%94%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E5%83%8F%E4%B8%AD%E7%97%9B1000%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"eab52e4ee106562d657bf9700b07a7f2e4a8f386","tid":2360864,"uid":316152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:15:18.000Z","msg":"想係佢下面出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf07b230c34f5cb4587b18b75dd816cf9d660bb8","tid":2360864,"uid":229397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"即係....佢原本覺得生B好似R痕咁樣既感覺?"},{"pid":"12871f2a8f56c7b69407ecd614d4f521e491b61c","tid":2360864,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf07b230c34f5cb4587b18b75dd816cf9d660bb8","tid":2360864,"uid":229397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"即係....佢原本覺得生B好似R痕咁樣既感覺?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"痾屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a5e534b38a570778c69a1229b69c213592318b","tid":2360864,"uid":127425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"點解唔直播生B"},{"pid":"17af2568b1c906c3032a579a87d6b38d13557ec0","tid":2360864,"uid":35930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy